channel.title: Windows Vista
channel.description: Okay I'm using Windows Vista to code my server source and I'm wondering if you can get the server online with Vista. I have heard different answers and I'm still not sure if you can! I'm not having much luck the server online right now. I have portfowarded, I have No-ip running, I am logged into the server using the blank Ip, I have added my port to the Windows and Firewall and I still can't get it online. I'm using a Linksys router and its still not working. Any suggestions here?[br][br][size=1]Posted on: August 24, 2008, 11:52:25 am[/size][hr]WTF! Every single time I need help no one responds to my threads. Omg...
